==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Guereza
<hw>Gue*re"za</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
beautiful Abyssinian monkey (<spn>Colobus guereza</spn>), having the
body black, with a fringe of long, silky, white hair along the sides,
and a tuft of the same at the end of the tail. The frontal band, cheeks,
and chin are white.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>gueridon</ent>⟦br⟧
